{"tid":230483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"心醉換來心碎，心碎過後還是等！","createTime":"2017-05-05T11:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T12:08:46.000Z","uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e1e0cf1a9ba18e460317468d306f78963b8cc9","tid":230483,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"燈光熄滅了，音樂靜止了 ，<br />\n滴下的眼淚已停不住了。<br />\n天下起雨了，人是不快樂 ，<br />\n我的心真的受傷了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n付出與收穫從來不成正比！<br />\n即使她知你對佢好，<br />\n但你付出了多少，她卻永遠不知道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儘管你能為她犧牲所有。<br />\n「所有」對她來説，也許只是一個數字，<br />\n她卻不知道是你的一切。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj